Detailed Description

cvmx_pip_alt_skip_cfg#

Notes: The actual SKIP I determined by HW is based on the packet contents. BIT0 and BIT1 make up a two value value that the selects the skip value as follows.

lookup_value = LEN ? ( packet_in_bits[BIT1], packet_in_bits[BIT0] ) : ( 0, packet_in_bits[BIT0] ); SKIP I = lookup_value == 3 ? SKIP3 : lookup_value == 2 ? SKIP2 : lookup_value == 1 ? SKIP1 : PIP_PRT_CFG<pknd>[SKIP];
